Hey there,

It's Eric from Firecrawl. I wanted to let you know that we're simplifying o=
ur pricing.

We've consolidated everything into one unified credit system. Credits now w=
ork across all endpoints (scrape, crawl, map, search, and extract).

With this change, Extract now uses credits at 15 tokens =3D 1 credit. If yo=
u're on an existing Extract plan, your tokens still work plus you can now u=
se them everywhere.

Check out our updated pricing page ( https://www.firecrawl.dev/pricing ) an=
d reach out to help@firecrawl.dev if you have any questions!

Best,

